column5: A long term project for sure.Been going on for 6 years now,trying to make the same tree twice.Like a big ass bonzai.  Sorry bout all the other stuff going on in the pic,just life around here. Joe
I love those trees, looks good.  Nice chicken too  Joey
I just wanna know how he gets Art to stand still so long.. and so tall !!!
I'm wondering about the 2 outdoor toilets...his n hers?
Planters for herbs,basil,parsley,thyme and rosemary.Keeps them from going crazy and taking over the garden. Joe
Amazing that a little balckmail goes such a long way.I had a chicken roosting on him and he still stayed in charactor. Joe
